Subject: [PATCH] spi: bcm63xx-hsspi: fix missing clk_disable_unprepare() on
 error in bcm63xx_hsspi_resume
Patch-mainline: v5.10.4
References: openEuler-21.03

stable inclusion
from stable-5.10.4
commit b8c65a716e8d862210394d76d492e0dc74f31ac3
